page.title: 19NATURE STUDY
page.content: NATURE STUDY IN EAST KILBRIDE We have been bird watching in Calderglen Country Park and so far we have seen BLACKBIRDS,BUZZARD,CHAFFINCH,CROW_ CARRION_HOODED,DIPPER,DUNNOCK,FLY- CATCHER_SPOTTED,GOLDCREST,GOLDFINCH, GREENFINCH,GULL_BLACKHEADED_COMMON GREAT BLACK BACKED_HERRING_LESSER, HERON,HOUSE MARTIN,JACKDAW,KESTREL, KINGFISHER,LAPWING,MAGPIE,MALLARD DUCK,OWL_BARN_TAWNY_SHORT_EARED, OYSTERCATCHER,PARTRIDGE,PHEASANT, PIGEON_WOOD,PIPPIT_MEADOW_TREE,RED WING,ROBIN,ROOK,SEDGE-WARBLER,SPARROW HAWK,SPARROW_COMMON_HOUSE,STARLING, SWALLOW,SKYLARK,THRUSH_MISTLE_SONG TIT_BLUE_COAL_GREAT_LONG-TAILED,TREE CREEPER,WAGTAIL_GREY_RED,WILLOWWARBLER WOODPECKER_GREAT SPOTTED,WREN. The dawn chorus on April 6th was started by a blackbird at 4.l5 a.m.
